column2: SELECT top # b.objid, m.BOSS_HEADS_DEC as dec, m.BOSS_HEADS_RA as ra, b.distance, G.psfMag_g - G.psfMag_i as Colour, G.psfMag_g from MyDB.RA_AND_DEC m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(m.BOSS_HEADS_RA,m.BOSS_HEADS_DEC, .#) b   join PhotoObj as G   ON G.objid = b.objid    WHERE b.distance < .#     AND G.type = #    AND G.psfMag_g < # ORDER BY b.distance
